OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An emergency alert being tested later  
OL,6, could be the sound that "saves your    
OL,7, life", the UK's deputy prime minister  
OL,8, has said.                              
OL,10,FPeople across the UK will hear a loud  
OL,11,Falarm on their phones for about 10     
OL,12,Fseconds on Sunday at 15:00 BST.        
OL,14,FOliver Dowden said no action from the  
OL,15,Fpublic will be needed, although some   
OL,16,Fsporting events and theatre shows will 
OL,17,Fbe paused during the test event.       
OL,19,FThe new system will be used in cases of
OL,20,Fflooding, wildfires or terror attacks. 
